			<link>http://www.chinacno.org/knowledges/instruments/弹/216-月琴</link>
			<guid isPermaLink="true">http://www.chinacno.org/knowledges/instruments/弹/216-月琴</guid>
			<description><![CDATA[<p>
	月琴，从阮演变而来。自晋代起就在民间流行，约从唐代起就有月琴之名，取其形圆似月、声如琴。</p>
]]></description>
			<author>xiaowenli@chinacno.org (肖文礼)</author>
