			<guid isPermaLink="true">http://www.chinacno.org/knowledges/instruments/弹/197-扬琴</guid>
			<description><![CDATA[<p>
	击弦乐器。又名洋琴、打琴。广泛应用于民歌、戏曲、曲艺伴奏，也用于器乐合奏和独奏。</p>
]]></description>
			<author>xiaowenli@chinacno.org (肖文礼)</author>
